> I have come to Mars to die. To be buried in the red sand.

> But Mars has other plans for me. It is a world of surprises.

> It is a world of beauty and terror. A world of life and death.

> And it is a world that is worth fighting for.

> ...a new reason to live... a new hope for the future...
